Burna Boy’s Mother Bose Ogulu accepted his Best International Act Award at the 2019 BET Award in US. While accepting the Award, she gave a moving speech calling on all black people to embrace their ‘Africannes.’ The speech received a standing ovation and has been trending on social media. See the video below: ICYMI: The moment @burnaboy was announced as winner of the @betawards Best International Act #BETAwards. Big love mama Burna ❤️ pic.twitter.com/EPJXlqNkc7